zadar.hr/ Official website] |notes = }} 'Zadar' (, historically known by other
names) is a city in Croatia on the Adriatic Sea. It is the centre of Zadar
County and the wider northern Dalmatian region. Zadar is a historical center of
Dalmatia as well as the seat of the Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Zadar.
